thread.title: Sen. Paul forces delay in voting on budget deal

title: Sen. Paul forces delay in voting on budget deal
text:
Sen. Paul forces delay in voting on budget deal Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:23 
Hopes for a quick vote on legislation to keep the U.S. government operating beyond midnight hit a snag on Thursday when Republican Senator Rand Paul put up a roadblock to voting because he first wanted debate on his amendment to kill the measure's increased federal spending. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
